title: What You Know 'Bout Love?

description:
Just call Jess the Love Doctor! In this episode, Jess gets real with her listeners and their love lives. She also gives her take on some celebrity relationships. Get your tea ...and maybe a pen and paper to keep a couple notes because you might just need this advice!
